---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Scenario Analysis: Multiple Futures, Honest Probabilities"
  description="Scenario-based analysis of Ghana's economy. Multiple possible futures with probability estimates, indicator watchlists, and audience-specific implications."
  keywords="Ghana economic scenarios, Ghana economy forecast 2026, Ghana policy scenarios, Ghana investment risk scenarios"
>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-label">Multiple Futures</div>
      <h1>Scenario Analysis</h1>
      <p>Preparing for multiple futures is smarter than betting on one forecast. Each scenario analysis models 3 to 5 possible paths with honest probability estimates.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Coming Soon</div>
        <div class="section-title">In Development</div>
        <div class="section-desc">Scenario analyses are advancing through the v3.0 publishing pipeline. The first scenario article is in development.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag scenario">Scenario Analysis</span>
          <h3>Ghana's Triple Shock: Three Scenarios for 2026</h3>
          <p>Hormuz oil crisis, cocoa financing collapse, and GSE correction hit simultaneously. Base case (40-50%), upside (15-25%), downside (30-40%), and wildcard scenarios with indicator watchlists.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">Stage 1 of 8</span>
            <span>Target: April 2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
